^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Most people play new minor forcing. And if you play New Minor Forcing then 2@H shows a ^*Bweak^*N hand with 5 spades and 4 (occasionally 5) hearts. Then the 1N bidder must either pass or correct. |
