PG| ***** 55 ***** |


NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|However, the 5-3 fit is much safer, because you can handle a 4-1 break much more easily and 4-1 breaks do happen 1/3 of the time. I personally bid 2@S rather than 2@H when I have both majors.|
