^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Well played Ann. Now lets talk about Ann's 1NT bid. It is obviously an off shape 1NT bid. Sometimes it is the best from among the alternatives, even though 1NT should promise at least 2 spades. However, on this hand I think there are 2 slightly better alternatives, although not clearly better. |
