NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|She only has 14 HCP, and usually you need more to reverse. If you use Bergen Starting Points, you can add 2 for the 2 quality suits and 1 for the club length, making the hand worth 17. And 17 is certainly enough to justify a reverse. |
