NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|If we change the hand a little, say @Sx @HAJ10x @DAxx @C KJxxx then 1N could very well be the best alternative. With that hand, Ann is clearly too weak to reverse, and her clubs are so-so so 1N seems like a reasonable alternative to 2@C.|
